code: @Override public DataSet<Edge<K, Tuple2<EV, Degrees>>> runInternal(Graph<K, VV, EV> input) throws Exception {     // s, d(s)     DataSet<Vertex<K, Degrees>> vertexDegrees = input.run(new VertexDegrees<K, VV, EV>().setParallelism(parallelism)).     // s, t, d(s)     return input.getEdges().join(vertexDegrees, JoinHint.REPARTITION_HASH_SECOND).where(0).equalTo(0).with(new JoinEdgeWithVertexDegree<>()).setParallelism(parallelism).name("Edge source degrees"). }
